anywhere but here is a 1999 american coming-of-age comedy-drama film , based on the novel of the same name by mona simpson . the screenplay was written by alvin sargent , and the film was directed by wayne wang . it was produced by laurence mark , petra alexandria , and ginny nugent . it stars susan sarandon , natalie portman , and shawn hatosy . filming began in late june 1998 . the film debuted at the toronto international film festival on september 17 , 1999 , before being released in the united states on november 12 .